item.title: About me
item.description: Hello there! My name is Jianhao and I am a software engineer based in Singapore. I have a strong passion for systems reliability, automation, performance and believe that a product is only as good as how reliable it is for its users. Also a Marvel fan, food lover, competitive swimmer/lifesaver, aquascaper. Memory isn’t my greatest strength, hence the existence of this page which serves as my HA knowledge dumping ground.
